title: Bug 116609 - [Regression] Color orange doesn't work
description:
Description: When trying to use the color orange, it doesn't work.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the application.
2. Go to the color selection menu.
3. Choose the color orange.
4. Apply the color to an element.

OB: When applying the orange color, it doesn't change the element color.
EB: When applying the orange color, the element color should change to orange.
SR: 1. Open the application.
2. Go to the color selection menu.
3. Choose the color orange.
4. Apply the color to an element.
5. Verify that the element color changes to orange.
